Vento Furniture, a premium furniture company in Nigeria, has partnered with Ali Nuhu, Kannywood actor, on ‘ALAQA’, a web series set for release on December 1, 2021. Nuhu is a Nigerian actor better known for his roles in both Hausa and English movies. Speaking at the sponsorship signing ceremony, Moaz Elhad, the company’s business manager, said that Vento Furniture identified with the Ali Nuhu brand in bringing undiluted entertainment to the northern audience in the country. From L-R: Sadiq Mahmood, Vento Furniture Legal adviser, Ramadan Booth Kannywood Actor, Ali Nuhu, Kannywood Actor and Moaz Elhad, Business Manager, Vento Furniture, at the sponsorship signing ceremony between Vento Furniture and FKD Productions for the upcoming ALAQA WEB Series. He described Ali Nuhu as a household name in the Kannywood entertainment industry who recognises the importance of promoting good values in society as evident in the ALAQA web series. “We at Vento Furniture identify with notable initiatives, and the ALAQA web series is one of such, hence our decision to be a part of it,” Elhad said. “The script is rich and highlights the merits of hard work, which forms parts of the hallmark of Vento Furniture.” <img class="wp-image-632681 size-large" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Ali-Nuhu-4-1024x576.jpg" alt="" width="900" height="506" srcset="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Ali-Nuhu-4-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Ali-Nuhu-4-300x169.jpg 300w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Ali-Nuhu-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Ali-Nuhu-4-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Ali-Nuhu-4-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Ali-Nuhu-4-24x14.jpg 24w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Ali-Nuhu-4-36x20.jpg 36w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Ali-Nuhu-4-48x27.jpg 48w" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px" /> Ali Nuhu, Kannywood actor. In his remarks, Nuhu thanked the management of Vento Furniture for identifying with the ALAQA web series through sponsorship. “On behalf of FKD Productions, I express my gratitude to Vento Furniture for identifying with such a noble project, and the northern audience should expect nothing but the best,” the actor added.